title: The Draymond Green Show - Warriors Back In The Finals
itunes:title: The Draymond Green Show - Warriors Back In The Finals
description:
Draymond Green discusses the Warriors beating the Mavericks in Game 5 to return to the NBA Finals for the sixth time in eight years, who their potential opponent could be, why Stephen A. Smith has some "new media" in him, and more. #Herd

Produced by: Jackson Safon
